just use a normal issue-based layer worktree?\n- Should the skill's allowlist entry in `worktree_create.sh` be removed if it can't work with `--type workspace`?\n\n## Affected Files\n\n- `.claude/skills/gather-project-knowledge/SKILL.md` — skill definition\n- `.agent/scripts/worktree_create.sh` — `ALLOWED_SKILLS` allowlist\n- `.agent/templates/knowledge_update_issue.md` — issue template\n- `.agent/scripts/setup.sh` — symlink creation logic\n\n---\n**Authored-By**: `Claude Code Agent`\n**Model**: `Claude Opus 4.6`","files":null}]}